lish and French, participate in an art auction, take a tourist tour with virtual reality glasses or travel - also virtually - to the ", "type": "text"}, {"url": "https://es.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dodona", "type": "link", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": "oracle of Dodona", "type": "text"}]}, {"text": " , where they wrote their questions with styluses on tablets and learned what the oracles were for and what they were asked.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "In the more practical part, there were informative talks on topics of interest such as the", "type": "text"}, {"url": "https://www.uam.es/uam/evau", "type": "link", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": " EvAU 2024", "type": "text"}]}, {"text": " , in which students' questions will be answered and guidelines will be given to the school counselors. There was also a challenge to revise a text translated by Artificial Intelligence (AI) as human correctors and Picamates will be discovered , sessions where mathematical tasks are proposed such as games, escape rooms, geometric constructions, origami... The objective of these activities was to discover aspects related to the studies and find the one that can best adapt to the needs of each person.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Robotics activity at Open House Day 2023. / UAM", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Other days", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "For those interested in studying Medicine or Nursing, the ", "type": "text"}, {"bold": true, "text": "Open Day", "type": "text"}, {"text": " of the ", "type": "text"}, {"bold": true, "text": "Medical Campus", "type": "text"}, {"text": " will be held on ", "type": "text"}, {"bold": true, "text": "Tuesday, April 23", "type": "text"}, {"text": ". At this event, information will be provided on the functioning of the center in the different teaching areas linked to the degrees of ", "type": "text"}, {