ernships and graduate programs. In addition, it allows attendees to learn about the latest trends in the labor market and strategies to be able to carry out an effective job search.  ", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "This University Employment Forum is the oldest and most prestigious in Spain, said the Vice-Rector for Students and Employability of the UAM , ", "type": "text"}, {"bold": true, "text": "Javier Oubia", "type": "text"}, {"text": ". In this twentieth edition, we continue to support employability as one of the fundamental values of our students training, he said. According to updated data from the  ", "type": "text"}, {"url": "https://obs-empleabilidad.uam.es/", "type": "link", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": "Employment Observatory", "type": "text"}]}, {"text": " , ", "type": "text"}, {"bold": true, "text": "8 out of 10 graduates of a Bachelors degree, 9 out of 10 Masters and Own Degrees and 10 out of 10 Doctorate graduates enter the labour market at the UAM", "type": "text"}, {"text": ". In addition, the average time of active search for recent graduates who have not previously worked is between two and three months and ", "type": "text"}, {"bold": true, "text": "80% of graduates of a Bachelors degree, postgraduate degree and doctorate degree consider that the UAM has contributed to improving their employability.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Access to the UAM Employment Forum is always free of charge. However, some activities are exclusively aimed at UAM members, currently enrolled students and AlumniUAM members.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The ", "type": "text"}, {"url": "https://foroempleouam.easyvirtualfair.com/webcasts", "type": "link", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": "programme ", "type": "text"}]}, {"text": "designed by the ", "type": "text"}, {"url": "https://www.uam.es/uam/oficina-practicas-externas", "type": "link", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": "Office of Internships and Employability (OPE)", "type": "text"}]}, {"text": ", which reports to the Vice-Rectorate of Studies and Employability, has been very comprehensive in this edition that ends today. Among many others, it has included two new activities, a  ", "type": "text"}, {"url": "https://foroempleouam.easyvirtualfair.com/resources/private/documents/Cafes_con_candidatos.pdf", "type": "link", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": "Caf Meeting for Students and Graduates", "type": "text"}]}, {"text": ",  where it has been possible to establish contact with representatives of human resources from the different entities that have participated in the Forum and a practical workshop, ", "type": "text"}, {"bold": true, "text": " Learn to use LinkedIn,", "type": "text"}, {"text": "  through which they have been able to discover all the advantages of this social network and boost their professional career using networking skills .", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "list", "format": "unordered", "children": [{"type": "list-item", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}, {"url": "https://youtu.be/xAvdyHzf9yE", "type": "link", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": "The forum on video", "type": "text"}]}, {"text": "", "type": "text"}]}]}, {"type": "list", "format": "unordered", "children": [{"type": "list-item", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}, {"url": "https://www.telemadrid.es/programas/madrid-trabaja/Comienza-el-Foro-de-Empleo-de-la-Autonoma-de-Madrid-el-mas-antiguo-de-las-universidades-madrilenas-9-2650624932--20240311044409.html", "type": "link", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": "Interview on Onda Madrid (Telemadrid) with the Vice-Rector for Students and Employability of the UAM, Javier Oubia .", "type": "text"}]}, {"text": "", "type": "text"}]}]}, {"type": "list", "format": "unordered", "children": [{"type": "list-item", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}, {"url": "https://www.madridnorte24horas.com/podcast/universidad-autonoma-