ola imparable de la transformacin digital, fortaleciendo as todas nuestras reas de conocimiento, dijo. ", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "El acto concluy con la interpretacin del himno de la universidad, Gaudeamus igitur, interpretado por el Coro de la UAM.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "El nuevo director de la EPS, Carlos Aguirre Maeso, se licenci en Ciencias (Matemticas) por la UAM en 1989 y se doctor en Informtica por esta misma universidad en el ao 2002. De 1989 a 2000 trabaj como analista en el Instituto de Ingeniera del Conocimiento (IIC). Ha sido profesor visitante en el Institute for Nonlinear Science (San Diego, EE UU), Zentrum fur Interdisciplinare Forschung (Bielefeld, Alemania) y Complexo Interdisiplinar da Universidade de Lisboa (Lisboa, Portugal). Actualmente es profesor contratado doctor en el Departamento de Ingeniera Informtica de la UAM. Sus principales reas de inters son el anlisis y estudio de redes complejas, el anlisis y estudio de seales biolgicas, el desarrollo de herramientas para el anlisis de datos y el estudio de fenmenos atmosfricos en Marte. Ha publicado ms de 30 artculos en revistas internacionales y ha participado en ms de 20 proyectos de investigacin nacionales e internacionales. Dilogo, apoyo a la investigacin, fomento del talento, mejora de la calidad docente e impulso a la participacin estudiantil son algunos de sus retos para esta nueva etapa.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Ms informacin", "type": "text"}]}]	2024-11-21 11:32:59.263	2024-11-26 19:29:30.13	2024-11-26 19:29:30.147	2	1	es	La secretaria general, Alma Rodrguez; la rectora Amaya Mendikoetxea
122	yf75100tu8n5yoltwpwip71m	Professor Carlos Aguirre Maeso takes office as director of the Higher Polytechnic School (EPS-UAM)	The new director said at the inauguration ceremony presided over by the rector Amaya Mendikoetxea that he felt honoured to occupy this position and hoped to be able to meet the expectations of those who supported his election. Enormous generosity in effort and working to achieve common goals is something that defines this Polytechnic School, he said in his speech.	2024-04-08	[{"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Carlos Aguirre Maeso, mathematician and professor of the Department of Computer Engineering, has taken the oath of office as director of the Higher Polytechnic School (EPS-UAM) at an event held last Friday in the Graduation Hall of this center.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "A broad representation of the university community headed by the rector Amaya Mendikoetxea, who presided over the ceremony, met to bid farewell to the outgoing director, Jos Mara Martnez Snchez, and welcome the new director of the EPS. Vice-rectors, the general director of the FUAM, the ombudsman of the University, the general secretary, the manager, deans, family and friends supported the new director at the beginning of this stage.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "EPS director Carlos Aguirre during his speech. / UAM", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "In his speech, Aguirre (along with these lines) said he felt honoured to occupy the position of director of this School, where he has developed his professional career. I have always wanted to stay here and chance came to my aid to be able to remain in what I proudly consider my university , he said. He also expressed his desire to be able to meet the expectations of all those people who supported him in his choice. A huge generosity in effort and working to achieve common goals is something that defines this Higher Polytechnic School, he said. He also wanted to thank all those in attendance, the outgoing director and the team that accompanies me in this life adventure that I began at the age of 18 at this university, as well as his family and those attending the event.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The rector Amaya Mendikoetxea began her speech by recalling what an Inauguration Ceremony symbolises: transfer of authority, legitimisation of the position, commitment to responsibilities, institutional continuity and representation of values, principles and leadership. She also had some emotional words for the outgoing director Jos Mara Martnez. Allow me to thank you again for your effort, your commitment and dedication during these difficult years that we have had to live through, part of which we have gone through together. Thank you, Chema, to you and your team for your involvement, which I am sure is a seed that has borne fruit and will continue to grow, she said. ", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The rector Amaya Mendikoetxea, during her speech. / UAM", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "He then addressed his words to the new director. Dear Carlos, beyond what you have proposed in your program, the application of technologies to society with a broader perspective is the challenge that I would like you and your team to take on. He also urged them to go further in this objective. I ask you to make the most of the tremendous potential of your disciplines and aim high, from the vocation of public service and without losing sight of the applications to business and society in general, to help us join the unstoppable wave of digital transformation, thus strengthening all our areas of knowledge, he said. ", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The event concluded with the performance of the university anthem, Gaudeamus igitur, performed by the UAM Choir.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The new director of the EPS, Carlos Aguirre Maeso, graduated in Sciences (Mathematics) from the UAM in 1989 and received his PhD in Computer Science from the same university in 2002. From 1989 to 2000 he worked as an analyst at the Institute for Knowledge Engineering (IIC). He has been a visiting professor at the Institute for Nonlinear Science (San Diego, USA), Zentrum fur Interdisciplinare Forschung (Bielefeld, Germany) and Complexo Interdisiplinar da Universidade de Lisboa (Lisbon, Portugal). He is currently a contracted professor with a PhD in the Department of Computer Engineering at the UAM. His main areas of interest are the analysis and study of complex networks, the analysis and study of biological signals, the development of tools for data analysis and the study of atmospheric phenomena on Mars. He has published more than 30 articles in international journals and has participated in more than 20 national and international research projects. Dialogue, support for research, fostering talent, improving teaching quality and encouraging student participation are some of the challenges for this new stage.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "More information", "type": "text"}]}]	2024-11-21 11:34:53.731	2024-11-26 19:29:54.65	2024-11-26 19:29:54.667	2	1	en	The general secretary, Alma Rodrguez; the rector Amaya Mendikoetxea;
123	qqehiouffbiocygp9dn0e4ag	La Ctedra UAM-EducAccin abre nuevos horizontes en la innovacin y el enfoque ESG en el mbito educativo	La Ctedra UAM-EducAccin, presentada ayer, tiene por objetivo trazar nuevos caminos hacia una educacin ms justa, equitativa y sostenible y medir el impacto en las reas ambiental, social y de gobernanza. Ser una plataforma para discutir y promover nuevas orientaciones para un mejor Sistema Educativo en Espaa.	2024-04-04	[{"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "La ", "type": "text"}, {"url": " http://www.uam.es/", "type": "link", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": "Universidad Autnoma de Madrid (UAM)", "type": "text"}]}, {"text": " y ", "type": "text"}, {"url": "https://www.educaccion.org/", "type": "link", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": "EducAccin", "type": "text"}]}, {"text": " se han unido para impulsar la innovacin y el impacto social, medioambiental y de gobernanza (Enviromental, Social y Governance, ESG) en el mbito educativo. Este esfuerzo conjunto se ha materializado en la Ctedra EducAccin en Impacto Ambiental, Social y de Gobernanza en el Sector Educativo, que tiene como objetivo fundamental trazar nuevos caminos hacia una educacin ms justa, equitativa y sostenible.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "El acto de presentacin, celebrado ayer, reuni a destacados lderes acadmicos y expertos en Educacin en nuestro pas. Asistieron el vicerrector de Transferencia, Innovacin y Cultura de la UAM, Flix Zamora; el director general de la FUAM, Fidel Rodrguez Batalla; el director de la ctedra, Santiago Atrio; la presidenta del Comit Cientfico de la ctedra, Sonia Dez; y el codirector de la ctedra, Jos Pic. El evento tambin cont con la presencia del filsofo y pedagogo Jos Antonio Marina y del presidente de la Fundacin Cultura de Paz, Federico Mayor Zaragoza, entre otras personalidades relevantes.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "La creacin de esta ctedra marca el comienzo de una nueva era en la educacin y se presenta como una plataforma para discutir y promover nuevas orientaciones para el futuro de este importante motor social.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Desde la Universidad Autnoma de Madrid hasta las instituciones y empresas colaboradoras, todos se han unido en este esfuerzo conjunto para redefinir el papel de la educacin en la sociedad. Desde su organizacin, se invita cordialmente a participar en este debate crucial a todas aquellas personas comprometidas con el futuro del aprendizaje y el bienestar de las generaciones venideras.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "En palabras de Sonia Dez, presidenta del Comit Cientfico de la ctedra: En un mundo donde la calidad educativa se ha medido tradicionalmente por parmetros acadmicos, la Ctedra EducAccin propone una visin revolucionaria. La calidad de la educacin va ms all de las calificaciones de los estudiantes y debe medirse por su impacto en las reas ambiental, social y de gobernanza.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Al adoptar el enfoque de \\"doble materialidad\\" en su reporting anual, la educacin se alinea con estndares internacionales de otros sectores, lo que permite una evaluacin ms holstica de su verdadero valor y costo. Esta iniciativa pionera busca destacar el coste de oportunidad de una educacin deficiente y promover prcticas que contribuyan a un sistema educativo ms slido y sostenible.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}, {"url": "https://fuam.es/catedras/", "type": "link", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": "Ms informacin ", "type": "text"}]}, {"text": "", "type": "text"}]}]	2024-11-21 11:24:47.849	2024-11-26 19:30:35.09	2024-11-26 19:30:35.104	2	1	es	Los responsables de la Ctedra UAM-EducAccin, tras el acto de presentacin. 
124	qqehiouffbiocygp9dn0e4ag	The UAM-EducAccin Chair opens new horizons in innovation and the ESG approach in the educational field	The UAM-EducAccin Chair, launched yesterday, aims to chart new paths towards a more just, equitable and sustainable education and to measure the impact in the environmental, social and governance areas. It will be a platform to discuss and promote new directions for a better Educational System in Spain.	2024-04-04	[{"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The Autonomous University of Madrid (UAM) and EducAccin have joined forces to promote innovation and social, environmental and governance ( ESG) impact in the educational field. This joint effort has materialized in the EducAccin Chair in Environmental, Social and Governance Impact in the Education Sector, which has the fundamental objective of charting new paths towards a more just, equitable and sustainable education.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The presentation ceremony, held yesterday, brought together prominent academic leaders and experts in Education in our country. The event was attended by the Vice-Rector for Transfer, Innovation and Culture of the UAM, Flix Zamora; the General Director of the FUAM, Fidel Rodrguez Batalla; the Director of the Chair, Santiago Atrio; the President of the Scientific Committee of the Chair, Sonia Dez; and the Co-Director of the Chair, Jos Pic. The event was also attended by the philosopher and pedagogue Jos Antonio Marina and the President of the Culture of Peace Foundation, Federico Mayor Zaragoza, among other relevant personalities.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The creation of this chair marks the beginning of a new era in education and is presented as a platform to discuss and promote new directions for the future of this important social engine.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "From the Autonomous University of Madrid to the collaborating institutions and companies, everyone has joined in this joint effort to redefine the role of education in society. The organization cordially invites all those committed to the future of learning and the well-being of future generations to participate in this crucial debate.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "In the words of Sonia Dez, president of the Chair's Scientific Committee: In a world where educational quality has traditionally been measured by academic parameters, the EducAccin Chair proposes a revolutionary vision. The quality of education goes beyond student grades and must be measured by its impact on the environmental, social and governance areas . ", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "By adopting a dual materiality approach in its annual reporting , education is aligned with international standards for other sectors, allowing for a more holistic assessment of its true value and cost. This pioneering initiative seeks to highlight the opportunity cost of poor education and promote practices that contribute to a stronger and more sustainable education system.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "More information ", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}]}]	2024-11-21 11:26:15.384	2024-11-26 19:31:00.566	2024-11-26 19:31:00.582	2	1	en	The heads of the UAM-EducAccin Chair, after the presentation ceremony. 
