ios y Enseanza a Distancia de la Universidad de Cantabria; Margalida Furi, directora de UIBTalent Formacin Avanzada de la Fundacin Universidad-Empresa Islas Baleares; y Santiago Gutirrez, vicerrector de Postgrado y Formacin Permanente en la Universidad de Castilla-La Mancha.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "A lo largo de la sesin los integrantes han abordado cada uno de los ejes que articulan el documento, centrndose en los aspectos fundamentales que corresponden a la elaboracin, desarrollo y acreditacin de las microcredenciales como son el diseo y certificacin de los elementos que las componen, los niveles de cualificacin, el aseguramiento de calidad, el fomento de visibilidad, la necesidad de la implementacin de un programa nacional, su papel en la formacin para el empleo en el mbito laboral, y la introduccin de mecanismos que le permitan ser una formacin orientada al empleo.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Los retos a los que se enfrenta las microcredenciales universitarias dentro del contexto social tambin han estado presentes durante la jornada. Entre ellos se han destacado la burocratizacin, la incorporacin de tecnologas, las sinergias entre universidad y administraciones, la especializacin y motivacin del cuerpo docente, la detencin de necesidades formativas con estructuras estables y la conexin con las empresas, entre otros.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": "La UAM y la Red RUEPEP", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}, {"url": "https://ruepep.org/", "type": "link", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": "La Red RUEPEP", "type": "text"}]}, {"text": " (Red Universitaria de Estudios de Posgrado y Educacin Permanente) es una asociacin de la que forman parte universidades pblicas y privadas espaolas entre las que se encuentra la UAM desde 2010, ao de fundacin de la Red.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "El objetivo principal de la Red RUEPEP es el de promover el contacto entre las universidades espaolas en el tema especfico de los estudios de posgrado y educacin permanente tanto desde el punto de vista acadmico como el de su gestin especializada.", "type": "text"}]}]	2024-11-18 20:57:24.342	2024-11-26 19:31:32.033	2024-11-26 19:31:32.053	1	1	es	Isabel Alonso, vicerrectora de Estudios de Posgrado y Formacin Continua de la UAM, junto con la mesa de participantes en la presentacin del documento.
126	bsqd5j0vdajumkhwzg9wv0tn	The UAM hosts the presentation of the Crue-RUEPEP guide for the preparation of microcredentials	During the session, the common criteria established in the document 'Guidelines for the design and accreditation of university micro-credentials', prepared by CRUE-RUEPEP, were revealed. These types of qualifications are focused on the development of specific professional skills and meet the current needs of the labour market.\n\n	2024-03-11	[{"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The Auditorium of the", "type": "text"}, {"url": "https://www.uam.es/Profesorado/Home.htm", "type": "link", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": " Faculty of Teacher Training and Education of the Autonomous University of Madrid (UAM)", "type": "text"}]}, {"text": " was the setting for the presentation of the document ", "type": "text"}, {"bold": true, "text": "Guidelines for the design and accreditation of university microcredentials", "type": "text"}, {"text": ", prepared by three Crue-RUEPEP working groups (Quality, Microcredentials and Employment) which are also made up of those responsible for postgraduate studies and continuing education from more than 30 Spanish universities, both public and private.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Isabel Alonso, Vice-Rector for Postgraduate Studies and Continuing Education, welcomed the attendees and introduced the participants in the panel, which was made up of Nicols Rodriguez Garca, Vice-Rector for Postgraduate Studies and Own Courses at the University of Salamanca; Mara Valds Gzquez, Rector's Commissioner for the Postgraduate School and Teaching Quality at the University of Barcelona; Sandra Marcos, Director of the Technical Quality Unit at the Pontifical University of Salamanca; Jon Altuna, Academic Vice-Rector at the University of Mondragn; Vanesa Valero, Vice-Rector for Continuing Education at the University of Murcia; Mara Jos Gonzlez, Vice-Rector for Own Courses and Distance Learning at the University of Cantabria; Margalida Furi, Director of UIBTalent Advanced Training at the University-Business Foundation of the Balearic Islands; and Santiago Gutirrez, Vice-Rector for Postgraduate and Continuing Education at the University of Castilla-La Mancha.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Throughout the session, the members have addressed each of the axes that articulate the document, focusing on the fundamental aspects that correspond to the elaboration, development and accreditation of microcredentials such as the design and certification of the elements that compose them, the qualification levels, quality assurance, the promotion of visibility, the need to implement a national program, its role in training for employment in the workplace, and the introduction of mechanisms that allow it to be employment-oriented training.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The challenges faced by university micro-credentials within the social context were also present during the conference. Among them, the following were highlighted: bureaucratization, the incorporation of technologies, synergies between universities and administrations, the specialization and motivation of the teaching staff, the detection of training needs with stable structures and the connection with companies, among others.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": "The UAM and the RUEPEP Network", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}, {"url": "https://ruepep.org/", "type": "link", "children": [{"bold": true, "text": "The RUEPEP Network ", "type": "text"}]}, {"text": "(University Network of Postgraduate Studies and Continuing Education) is an association that includes Spanish public and private universities, including the UAM, since 2010, the year the Network was founded.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The main objective of the RUEPEP Network is to promote contact between Spanish universities on the specific subject of postgraduate studies and continuing education, both from an academic point of view and from that of their specialized management.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}]}]	2024-11-18 21:00:02.372	2024-11-26 19:31:59.337	2024-11-26 19:31:59.355	1	1	en	Isabel Alonso, Vice-Rector for Postgraduate Studies and Continuing Education at the UAM, together with the panel of participants at the presentation of the document.
127	e8zxujgkj8obfxe5bs2hf2lo	La UAM acoge la presentacin de las conclusiones del Proyecto de Inteligencia Institucional Universitaria  UNIDIGITAL	La jornada es la culminacin de una etapa de colaboracin entre universidades pblicas madrileas, en una iniciativa que representa su compromiso con la transformacin digital, la innovacin y la mejora continua.	2024-04-19	[{"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "La Universidad Autnoma de Madrid (UAM) ha acogido una jornada de presentacin de los resultados y conclusiones del proyecto colaborativo UNIDIGITAL Inteligencia Institucional Universitaria: Mejora de la capacidad analtica en las universidades para optimizar la toma de decisiones institucionales y mejorar los servicios. Este proyecto ha marcado un hito en la modernizacin y digitalizacin de las universidades participantes, a travs de la implementacin, soporte y evolucin de las plataformas de inteligencia institucional y otros servicios relacionados con la inteligencia de negocio (BI, Business Intelligence).", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "La rectora Amaya Mendikoetxea y el vicerrector de Planificacin y Estrategia Digital, Jess Bescs, con pblico alrededor.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "La rectora Amaya Mendikoetxea dio una clida bienvenida a los asistentes, subrayando que \\"las universidades tienen que ser actores centrales en los procesos de transformacin digital que se estn produciendo en nuestras sociedades.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "A continuacin, la Oficina Tcnica del proyecto present los objetivos y resultados principales, destacando los avances significativos en el anlisis de datos, la implantacin de infraestructura y el diseo e implementacin de sistemas analticos en varias reas clave de las universidades participantes.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "El eje principal de la sesin fue el anlisis detallado de los resultados y las conclusiones en las cuatro reas contempladas: Rendimiento Acadmico (liderado por la UAM), Doctorado (por la UAH), Econmico (por la UPM) y Recursos Humanos (por la URJC). Estas presentaciones no solo revelaron el progreso alcanzado en cada rea, sino que tambin generaron debates constructivos sobre cmo seguir avanzando en el futuro.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "A lo largo de la jornada, los participantes tuvieron la oportunidad de reflexionar sobre el impacto logrado en cada universidad y las perspectivas de futuro del proyecto, destacando la importancia de seguir promoviendo una cultura de toma de decisiones basada en datos y la colaboracin continua entre las universidades participantes.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Al acto acudieron destacados representantes de las universidades Politcnica, Alcal y Rey Juan Carlos, participantes junto a la UAM y la Carlos III en el proyecto, as como a expertos de lamo Consulting, socio tecnolgico adjudicatario de este proyecto.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Entre los asistentes se encontraban vicerrectores y vicegerentes, directores, analistas de datos, tcnicos de aplicaciones e investigadores, que comparten el compromiso con la transformacin digital y la mejora continua de la calidad educativa universitaria.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Este proyecto representa un salto significativo en la gestin analtica para las universidades participantes, estableciendo una slida base para futuros desarrollos. Segn explican sus responsables, los resultados brindan una base slida para seguir avanzando en esta lnea y en el prometedor desarrollo de soluciones de gestin apoyada por la IA: son un claro testimonio del compromiso de las universidades pblicas madrileas con la transformacin digital, la innovacin y la mejora continua.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "", "type": "text"}]}]	2024-11-21 11:58:50.476	2024-11-26 19:32:43.236	2024-11-26 19:32:43.251	2	1	es	Foto de familia de los asistentes al acto.
128	e8zxujgkj8obfxe5bs2hf2lo	The UAM hosts the presentation of the conclusions of the University Institutional Intelligence Project  UNIDIGITAL	The event is the culmination of a period of collaboration between public universities in Madrid, in an initiative that represents their commitment to digital transformation, innovation and continuous improvement.	2024-04-19	[{"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The Autonomous University of Madrid (UAM) has hosted a presentation day of the results and conclusions of the collaborative project UNIDIGITAL University Institutional Intelligence: Improving analytical capacity in universities to optimize institutional decision-making and improve services . This project has marked a milestone in the modernization and digitalization of the participating universities, through the implementation, support and evolution of institutional intelligence platforms and other services related to business intelligence (BI).", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Rector Amaya Mendikoetxea and Vice-Rector for Planning and Digital Strategy, Jess Bescs, with the public around them.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Rector Amaya Mendikoetxea warmly welcomed the attendees, stressing that \\"universities have to be central players in the digital transformation processes that are taking place in our societies.\\"", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The Technical Office of the project then presented the main objectives and results, highlighting the significant advances in data analysis, infrastructure implementation, and the design and implementation of analytical systems in several key areas of the participating universities.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The main focus of the session was the detailed analysis of the results and conclusions in the four areas covered: Academic Performance (led by the UAM), Doctorate (by the UAH), Economics (by the UPM) and Human Resources (by the URJC). These presentations not only revealed the progress achieved in each area, but also generated constructive debates on how to continue moving forward in the future.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Throughout the day, participants had the opportunity to reflect on the impact achieved at each university and the future prospects of the project, highlighting the importance of continuing to promote a culture of data-driven decision-making and ongoing collaboration between participating universities .", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "The event was attended by prominent representatives of the Polytechnic University, Alcal University and Rey Juan Carlos University, participants in the project alongside the UAM and Carlos III University, as well as experts from lamo Consulting, the technological partner awarded this project.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "Attendees included vice-rectors and vice-managers, directors, data analysts, application technicians and researchers, who share a commitment to digital transformation and the continuous improvement of the quality of university education.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "children": [{"text": "This project represents a significant leap forward in analytical management for the participating universities, establishing a solid foundation for future developments. According to those responsible, the results provide a solid basis for further progress in this line and in the promising development of AI-supported management solutions : they are a clear testament to the commitment of Madrid's public universities to digital transformation, innovation and continuous improvement.", "type": "text"}]}]	2024-11-21 12:00:19.783	2024-11-26 19:33:07.214	2024-11-26 19:33:07.228	2	1	en	Group photo of those attending the event.
